<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Stake Confirmation - DiTokens CRM</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
        }
        .header {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #3498db 0%, #2980b9 100%);
            color: white;
            padding: 40px 30px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .header h1 {
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 28px;
            font-weight: 300;
        }
        .content {
            padding: 40px 30px;
        }
        .success-message {
            background-color: #d4edda;
            border: 1px solid #c3e6cb;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .stake-details {
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            border: 2px solid #e9ecef;
            border-radius: 10px;
            padding: 30px;
            margin: 30px 0;
        }
        .detail-row {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            padding: 10px 0;
        }
        .detail-row.total {
            border-top: 2px solid #dee2e6;
            padding-top: 20px;
            margin-top: 20px;
            font-weight: bold;
            font-size: 18px;
        }
        .detail-label {
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #495057;
        }
        .detail-value {
            color: #6c757d;
        }
        .total .detail-value {
            color: #3498db;
            font-size: 20px;
        }
        .cta-button {
            display: inline-block;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #3498db 0%, #2980b9 100%);
            color: white;
            padding: 15px 30px;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 25px;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin: 20px 0;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .footer {
            background-color: #2c3e50;
            color: white;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 30px;
        }
        .status-badge {
            background-color: #3498db;
            color: white;
            padding: 8px 16px;
            border-radius: 20px;
            font-size: 14px;
            font-weight: 600;
            display: inline-block;
        }
        .reward-info {
            background-color: #e8f4fd;
            border: 1px solid #bee5eb;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .timeline {
            background-color: #fff3cd;
            border: 1px solid #ffeaa7;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .timeline-item {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }
        .timeline-icon {
            width: 30px;
            height: 30px;
            background-color: #3498db;
            border-radius: 50%;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            margin-right: 15px;
            color: white;
            font-size: 14px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>üîí Stake Confirmed!</h1>
            <p>Your tokens are now staked and earning rewards</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="content">
            <div class="success-message">
                <h2>Hello {{name}},</h2>
                <p>Excellent! Your staking request has been processed successfully. Your tokens are now locked in the staking pool and earning rewards.</p>
                <div class="status-badge">STAKED</div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="stake-details">
                <div class="detail-row">
                    <span class="detail-label">Stake Date:</span>
                    <span class="detail-value">{{stakeDate}}</span>
                </div>
                <div class="detail-row">
                    <span class="detail-label">Transaction ID:</span>
                    <span class="detail-value">{{transactionId}}</span>
                </div>
                <div class="detail-row">
                    <span class="detail-label">Staked Amount:</span>
                    <span class="detail-value">{{tokens}} tokens</span>
                </div>
                <div class="detail-row">
                    <span class="detail-label">Staking Period:</span>
                    <span class="detail-value">{{period}}</span>
                </div>
                <div class="detail-row">
                    <span class="detail-label">Annual Percentage Yield:</span>
                    <span class="detail-value">{{apy}}%</span>
                </div>
                <div class="detail-row">
                    <span class="detail-label">Lock Period:</span>
                    <span class="detail-value">{{lockPeriod}}</span>
                </div>
                <div class="detail-row total">
                    <span class="detail-label">Total Staked Value:</span>
                    <span class="detail-value">{{totalValue}}</span>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="reward-info">
                <h3>üí∞ Reward Information:</h3>
                <p><strong>Daily Rewards:</strong> Approximately {{dailyRewards}} tokens</p>
                <p><strong>Monthly Rewards:</strong> Approximately {{monthlyRewards}} tokens</p>
                <p><strong>Total Rewards ({{period}}):</strong> Approximately {{totalRewards}} tokens</p>
                <p><strong>Reward Distribution:</strong> Rewards are distributed daily at 00:00 UTC</p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="timeline">
                <h3>üìÖ Staking Timeline:</h3>
                <div class="timeline-item">
                    <div class="timeline-icon">‚úì</div>
                    <div>
                        <strong>Today:</strong> Tokens locked in staking pool
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="timeline-item">
                    <div class="timeline-icon">‚è∞</div>
                    <div>
                        <strong>Daily:</strong> Rewards accumulate and are distributed
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="timeline-item">
                    <div class="timeline-icon">üîì</div>
                    <div>
                        <strong>{{unlockDate}}:</strong> Staking period ends, tokens become available
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div style="text-align: center;">
                <a href="{{dashboardUrl}}" class="cta-button">View My Stakes ‚Üí</a>
            </div>
            
            <div style="background-color: #e8f5e8; padding: 20px; border-radius: 8px; margin: 20px 0;">
                <h4>üöÄ What happens next?</h4>
                <ul style="margin: 10px 0; padding-left: 20px;">
                    <li>Your tokens are now earning daily rewards</li>
                    <li>Rewards are automatically added to your staking balance</li>
                    <li>You can monitor your staking performance in real-time</li>
                    <li>At the end of the lock period, you can unstake or restake</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            
            <div style="background-color: #fff3cd; padding: 20px; border-radius: 8px; margin: 20px 0;">
                <h4>üí° Staking Tips:</h4>
                <ul style="margin: 10px 0; padding-left: 20px;">
                    <li>Longer staking periods typically offer higher APY</li>
                    <li>Consider compound staking for maximum returns</li>
                    <li>Monitor market conditions for optimal staking timing</li>
                    <li>Diversify your staking across different periods</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            
            <p style="color: #666; font-size: 14px; text-align: center;">
                <strong>Need help?</strong> Contact our support team at support@ditokens.com or visit our staking guide.
            </p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="footer">
            <p>¬© 2024 DiTokens CRM. All rights reserved.</p>
            <p style="font-size: 12px; color: #bdc3c7;">
                This email confirms your staking transaction. Please keep it for your records.
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
